snippet.title: Converting Decimals to Fractions [fbt]
snippet.description:
This video by Fort Bend Tutoring shows the process of converting decimals into fractions. Six (6) examples are shown in this FBT math tutorial. This video is instructed by Larry "Mr. Whitt" Whittington. Intro/Outro by Chuck Knipp's Shirley Q. Liquor.
